    • getSynonymousModelLevelRelationForSemSimOWLwriting

      public static Relation getSynonymousModelLevelRelationForSemSimOWLwriting​(Relation rel)
      Look up which relation to use for an ontology-level annotation in a SemSim OWL file. This is needed because the same OWL property can't be used in statements on classes and in ontology-level annotations.
      Parameters:
      rel - The Relation that we'd like to use for the ontology-level annotation
      Returns:
      The synonymous relation to use for the ontology-level annotation
